bill.summary: Directs the Clerk of the House of Representatives to make specified corrections in the enrollment of H.R. 1892 (Bipartisan Budget Act of 2018), including modifications to provisions relating to funding for: (1) the Joint Select Committee on Solvency of Multiemployer Pension Plans, and (2) the Joint Select Committee on Budget and Appropriations Process Reform.
